  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add ginger and scallions, sauté for about 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add fermented vegetables to the pan, mix well with rice wine vinegar.",
    "Gently fold in prosciutto slices, cooking until heated through but not crispy.",
    "Stir in fluffed pilaf rice blend and season with salt and pepper according to taste.",
    "Serve immediately."
